        Researching a Brisbane Suburb's Price Growth and Sales History Before Selling: What the Data Shows and What It Hides
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Two hours of research into your suburb's sales data saves weeks of campaign missteps. Here is how to read the public numbers, what the medians hide, and how to build a comparable sales list that actually helps you price and choose an agent.
      </p>
